        python3 scripts/zeta/write_file.py --path tmp/chatdev_smoke/HelloSimulatedVerse.md --content "# Hello from ChatDev smoke test\n\nThis artifact was generated by ChatDev smoke test on $$(date).\n\n**Status**: Local tools operational ✅\n**Mode**: Zero-token local operation\n**Integration**: SimulatedVerse Culture-Ship"

